ECB Methods
===========

 * The "ECB-Methods" buffer contains the methods (and variables, if you
   want) in the selected source file. When a method/variable is selected
   with the primary mouse button  or RETURN (*note Usage of ECB::) the
   edit buffer will jump to the method/variable.

 * Clicking on a method/variable with the secondary mouse button or
   C-RETURN (*note Usage of ECB::) will jump to the method in the other
   edit window.


